Introduction

Lusty (Korean: 러스티) was a South Korean girl group under BabaPlay. They made their debut on June 26, 2019 with the digital single "Thirsty".They disbanded sometime in 2021 with member Harin confirming the group's disbandment in an interview with Kpop Idol Olympic posted on January 2, 2023. Their name stands for "Lively, Sturdy, and Robust".
